{
  "page": "King of Meereen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:John_Goodenough_crown_of_MeereenIII.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/John_Goodenough_crown_of_MeereenIII.png/300px-John_Goodenough_crown_of_MeereenIII.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"196\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/John_Goodenough_crown_of_MeereenIII.png/450px-John_Goodenough_crown_of_MeereenIII.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/John_Goodenough_crown_of_MeereenIII.png/600px-John_Goodenough_crown_of_MeereenIII.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:John_Goodenough_crown_of_MeereenIII.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Ruby\" title=\"Ruby\">Ruby</a> crown of Meereen, by John Goodenough © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>King of Meereen</b> is a title used by <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereenese</a> monarchs of old.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The city is now ruled by <a href=\"/index.php/Slavers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slavers\">slavers</a> called the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Masters\" title=\"Great Masters\">Great Masters</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Known_monarchs_of_Meereen\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known monarchs of Meereen</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_Meereen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a>, it has been \"a thousand years\" since <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> last had a king.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-date_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-date-3\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_Meereen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_Meereen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dance_with_dragons_by_grr_martin_by_marcsimonetti-d84tlih.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/98/Dance_with_dragons_by_grr_martin_by_marcsimonetti-d84tlih.jpg/300px-Dance_with_dragons_by_grr_martin_by_marcsimonetti-d84tlih.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"415\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/98/Dance_with_dragons_by_grr_martin_by_marcsimonetti-d84tlih.jpg/450px-Dance_with_dragons_by_grr_martin_by_marcsimonetti-d84tlih.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/98/Dance_with_dragons_by_grr_martin_by_marcsimonetti-d84tlih.jpg/600px-Dance_with_dragons_by_grr_martin_by_marcsimonetti-d84tlih.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dance_with_dragons_by_grr_martin_by_marcsimonetti-d84tlih.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> in the audience chamber of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Pyramid\" title=\"Great Pyramid\">Great Pyramid</a>, by Marc Simonetti © LeYa Brasil</div></div></div>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Meereen\" title=\"Siege of Meereen\">takes Meereen</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Masters\" title=\"Great Masters\">Great Masters</a>, becoming <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">the city</a>'s new ruler.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_Meereen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Daenerys is introduced as \"Queen of Meereen\" as she holds court in the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Pyramid\" title=\"Great Pyramid\">Great Pyramid</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daenerys weds <a href=\"/index.php/Hizdahr_zo_Loraq\" title=\"Hizdahr zo Loraq\">Hizdahr zo Loraq</a>, through which he becomes Meereen's <a href=\"/index.php/King\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King\">king</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> After Daenerys disappears from <a href=\"/index.php/Daznak%27s_Pit\" title=\"Daznak&#39;s Pit\">Daznak's Pit</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a>, Hizdahr rules over the city as King of Meereen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Skahaz_mo_Kandaq\" title=\"Skahaz mo Kandaq\">Skahaz mo Kandaq</a> convinces Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> that Hizdahr played a part in the attempt on Daenerys's life.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Together with <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Worm\" title=\"Grey Worm\">Grey Worm</a>, Barristan and Skahaz arrest Hizdahr and install a council to rule the city in Daenerys's absence.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_monarchs_of_Meereen\">Known monarchs of Meereen</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_Meereen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known monarchs of Meereen\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Stormborn</a>, the First of Her Name, the Unburnt, Queen of Meereen, <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_the_Andals_and_the_Rhoynar_and_the_First_Men\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen of the Andals and the Rhoynar and the First Men\">Queen of the Andals and the Rhoynar and the First Men</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Lord of the Seven Kingdoms\">Lord of the Seven Kingdoms</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Protector_of_the_Realm\" title=\"Protector of the Realm\">Protector of the Realm</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Khaleesi_of_the_Great_Grass_Sea\" title=\"Khaleesi of the Great Grass Sea\"><i>Khaleesi</i> of Great Grass Sea</a>, Breaker of Shackles, and Mother of Dragons<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\"><img alt=\"Meereen.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/20px-Meereen.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/30px-Meereen.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/40px-Meereen.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Hizdahr_zo_Loraq\" title=\"Hizdahr zo Loraq\">Hizdahr zo Loraq</a>, Fourteenth of That Noble Name,<sup id=\"cite_ref-numeral_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-numeral-9\">&#91;N 2&#93;</a></sup> King of Meereen, <a href=\"/index.php/Scion_of_Ghis\" title=\"Scion of Ghis\">Scion of Ghis</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Octarch_of_the_Old_Empire\" title=\"Octarch of the Old Empire\">Octarch of the Old Empire</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_the_Skahazadhan\" title=\"Master of the Skahazadhan\">Master of the Skahazadhan</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Consort_to_Dragons\" title=\"Consort to Dragons\">Consort to Dragons</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Blood_of_the_Harpy\" title=\"Blood of the Harpy\">Blood of the Harpy</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_Meereen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-date-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-date_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">It is unknown if this means one thousand years ago - seven hundred years before <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a> - or if <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> is being figurative.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-numeral-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-numeral_9-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">It is unclear if this means there have been thirteen other Kings of Meereen named Hizdahr, if he is the fourteenth member of the House of Loraq by that name, or if he is the fourteenth Loraq to rule as King of Meereen.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_Meereen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd55.7B.7B.7B3.